README  

Overview
============

These are the exercises for the Operating Systems Laboratory course
of National Technical University of Athens (NTUA) 2012-2013.

exercise1: Implementation of a Linux character device driver

exercise2: Implementation of a Qemu virtual device and 
a simple TCP/IP communication (chat) using Linux sockets

Misc 
